title: Missing Summoner Icon Gifted from Friend
body:
Can't find my Blood Moon Yasuo Icon I've been used for a while, and in the store it shows up as an icon I don't own, with a 250rp price.
 
I checked the Gifting History and my friend gifted this to me on 11/17/16, I used it for about a month and switched to others.

replies.body: We'd like to look into this individually with you to see what's going on.  Hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new) so we can help!  We'll reply back asap!
